about.summary: A backport of recent additions to the `collections.abc` module.

name: backports_abc
raw_recipe:
{% set version="0.5" %}

package:
  name: backports_abc
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: backports_abc-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/b/backports_abc/backports_abc-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 033be54514a03e255df75c5aee8f9e672f663f93abb723444caec8fe43437bde

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - backports_abc

about:
  home: https://github.com/cython/backports_abc
  license: PSF 2
  summary: A backport of recent additions to the `collections.abc` module.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
